     <div id="welcomeblock">Welcome to The Dragon Ball Fanfiction Library, the oldest DB/DBZ/DBGT fanfic archive on the web! If you are an author who has work on this site and aren&#39;t in control of your account (but would like to be) please <a href="http://dbfl.gokugirl.com/contact.php">contact me</a>. Also, if you are an author from the old site whose account has not been created yet, how about doing me a favor and uploading your own stories? :)<br /><br />To sign up for an account so that you can submit stories, click &#39;register&#39; on the navigation menu. You don&#39;t need an account to read fanfiction.</div>
